1、yum 添加 阿里云源 http://mirrors.aliyun.com/help/centos
  1) mv /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo.backup 
  2) wget -O /etc/yum.repos.d/CentOS-Base.repo http://mirrors.aliyun.com/repo/Centos-7.repo
2、yum 添加 rpmfusion https://rpmfusion.org/Configuration
  1) sudo yum localinstall --nogpgcheck https://download1.rpmfusion.org/free/el/rpmfusion-free-release-7.noarch.rpm https://download1.rpmfusion.org/nonfree/el/rpmfusion-nonfree-release-7.noarch.rpm
3、firefox 添加 flash-player
  1) https://get.adobe.com/flashplayer/?loc=cn 下载flash player安装
  2) yum install flash-plugins 安装flash plugin
4、安装 mp3解码 
  1) yum 添加 rpmfusion
  2) yum install gstreamer-plugins-bad gstreamer-plugins-ugly

5、安装 ntfs-3g 识别 U盘格式ntfs
  1) yum install ntfs-3g

6、安装 mp4解码 方法1
  1) yum 添加 rpmfusion
  2) yum install gstreamer-plugins-bad gstreamer-plugins-ugly gstreamer-ffmpeg vlc
  3) 使用 vlc 来播放视频

7、安装 mp4解码 方法2
  1) yum 添加 rpmfusion
  2) yum install yum install gstreamer-plugins-bad gstreamer-plugins-ugly gstreamer-plugins-libav 
